basic.description:
{Mysticism — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 3 spell points per day (base 1 + 2 WOG bonus), plus natural recovery.

WOG Enhancement: +2 additional SP/day. Passive bonus applied each morning.

advanced.description:
{Mysticism — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 5 spell points per day (base 2 + 3 WOG bonus), plus natural recovery.

WOG Enhancement: +3 additional SP/day. Passive bonus applied each morning.

expert.description:
{Mysticism — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Regenerates 8 spell points per day (base 3 + 5 WOG bonus), plus natural recovery.

WOG Enhancement: +5 additional SP/day. Passive bonus applied each morning.

basic.description:
{Estates — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 125 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Generates hero_level × 5 additional gold per day (scales with hero level). A level 10 hero earns 50 extra gold/day.

advanced.description:
{Estates — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 250 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Generates hero_level × 8 additional gold per day. A level 10 hero earns 80 extra gold/day.

expert.description:
{Estates — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Generates 500 gold per day.

WOG Enhancement: Generates hero_level × 12 additional gold per day. A level 10 hero earns 120 extra gold/day.

basic.description:
{Learning — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 5% more experience from battles.

WOG Enhancement: Also gains 100 experience passively each day.

advanced.description:
{Learning — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 10% more experience from battles.

WOG Enhancement: Also gains 200 experience passively each day.

expert.description:
{Learning — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Hero gains 15% more experience from battles.

WOG Enhancement: Also gains 300 experience passively each day.

basic.description:
{Sorcery — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 10% (base 5% + WOG +5%).

WOG Enhancement: Sorcery I doubles the base spell damage bonus.

advanced.description:
{Sorcery — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 20% (base 10% + WOG +10%).

WOG Enhancement: Sorcery I doubles the base spell damage bonus.

expert.description:
{Sorcery — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Spell damage increased by 35% (base 15% + WOG +20%).

WOG Enhancement: Sorcery I and II combined. Expert-level destruction magic.

basic.description:
{Armorer — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 8% (base 5% + WOG +3%).

WOG Enhancement: Armorer I provides stronger physical protection.

advanced.description:
{Armorer — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 13% (base 10% + WOG +3%).

WOG Enhancement: Armorer I provides stronger physical protection.

expert.description:
{Armorer — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Damage received reduced by 20% (base 15% + WOG +5%).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Armorer — one fifth of all physical damage is negated.

basic.description:
{Resistance — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

10% chance to resist enemy spells (base 5% + WOG +5%).

WOG Enhancement: Resistance II doubles the magic resistance chance.

advanced.description:
{Resistance — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

15% chance to resist enemy spells (base 10% + WOG +5%).

WOG Enhancement: Resistance II increases magic resistance significantly.

expert.description:
{Resistance — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

30% chance to resist enemy spells (base 20% + WOG +10%).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Resistance — nearly one third of all spells are deflected.

basic.description:
{Navigation — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 60% (base 50% + WOG +10%).

WOG Enhancement: Navigation I provides improved sea travel efficiency.

advanced.description:
{Navigation — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 110% (base 100% + WOG +10%).

WOG Enhancement: Navigation I provides improved sea travel efficiency.

expert.description:
{Navigation — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Movement over water increased by 165% (base 150% + WOG +15%).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Navigation — maximum sea mobility.

basic.description:
{Eagle Eye — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

40% chance to learn spells of levels 1-2 used by enemies in battle.

WOG Enhancement: Can now learn level 3 spells. Chance increased to 50%.

advanced.description:
{Eagle Eye — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

50% chance to learn spells of levels 1-3 used by enemies in battle.

WOG Enhancement: Can learn level 4 spells. Chance increased to 65%.

expert.description:
{Eagle Eye — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

60% chance to learn spells of levels 1-4 used by enemies in battle.

WOG Enhancement: Can learn level 5 spells (including adventure map spells).

basic.description:
{Tactics — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Rearrange troops in a 3-hex-deep zone before battle (base 2).

WOG Enhancement: Tactics I extends the deployment zone by 1 hex.

advanced.description:
{Tactics — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Rearrange troops in a 4-hex-deep zone before battle (base 3).

WOG Enhancement: Tactics I extends the deployment zone by 1 hex.

expert.description:
{Tactics — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Rearrange troops in a 6-hex-deep zone before battle (base 5).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Tactics — near-full battlefield repositioning.

basic.description:
{Scholar — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Share level 1-2 spells with other heroes on the same tile.

WOG Enhancement: Scholar I allows sharing level 3 spells.

advanced.description:
{Scholar — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Share level 1-3 spells with other heroes.

WOG Enhancement: Scholar I allows sharing level 4 spells.

expert.description:
{Scholar — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Share level 1-4 spells with other heroes.

WOG Enhancement: Scholar I allows sharing level 5 spells — any spell can be taught.

basic.description:
{Scouting — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Increases hero's sight radius by 2 tiles (base 1).

WOG Enhancement: Scouting II doubles the sight radius increase.

advanced.description:
{Scouting — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Increases hero's sight radius by 3 tiles (base 2).

WOG Enhancement: Scouting II provides additional vision distance.

expert.description:
{Scouting — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Increases hero's sight radius by 5 tiles (base 3).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Scouting — broad map awareness.

basic.description:
{Pathfinding — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

Reduces rough terrain movement penalty by 35% (base 25%).

WOG Enhancement: Pathfinding I is more effective on difficult terrain.

advanced.description:
{Pathfinding — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

Reduces rough terrain movement penalty by 60% (base 50%).

WOG Enhancement: Pathfinding I is more effective on difficult terrain.

expert.description:
{Pathfinding — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

Reduces rough terrain movement penalty by 75% (base 75%).

WOG Enhancement: Expert Pathfinding — nearly all terrain types become passable.

basic.description:
{Luck — Basic [WOG Enhanced]}

+1 Luck to all troops. Lucky strike deals double damage.

WOG Enhancement: Luck I increases the frequency of lucky strikes.

advanced.description:
{Luck — Advanced [WOG Enhanced]}

+2 Luck to all troops. Lucky strike deals double damage.

WOG Enhancement: Luck I increases the frequency of lucky strikes.

expert.description:
{Luck — Expert [WOG Enhanced]}

+3 Luck to all troops. Lucky strike deals double damage.

WOG Enhancement: Expert Luck — fortune smiles upon your every engagement.
